<subSubSection pageId="569" pageNumber="570" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="569" pageNumber="570">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="569" pageNumber="570">This species ranges from Newfoundland (Lindroth 1955a: 100) to southeastern British Columbia (Lindroth 1968: 690), south to southern Colorado (Wickham 1902: 236; Armin 1963: 200), southeastern Kansas (Knaus 1907: 233), Missouri (Summers 1873: 145), and southwestern North Carolina (Macon County, MCZ). The record from southeastern Louisiana (Summers 1874a: 80) is likely in error.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
